# Privacy Policy

## Information Collection

At Yuotuop, we collect information that you provide to us and information that
we process in connection with our services.

This may include, but is not
limited to, URLs and related content for YouTube videos that you wish to
transcribe or analyze.

Our collection is focused solely on information
essential for the effective operation and enhancement of our services.

We are committed to using the information we collect responsibly and in
a manner that respects your privacy.
